---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="FAQ - Frequently Asked Questions About Meme Face | Meme Face"
	description="Find answers to frequently asked questions about Meme Face. Learn about downloading, using, and sharing meme faces. Get help with common issues and questions."
	keywords="meme face FAQ, frequently asked questions, meme face questions, meme face help, meme face support, meme face download, meme face usage, meme face guide"
>
	<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-indigo-100">
		<!-- Back to Home Link -->
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-6">
			<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-700 transition-colors">
				<svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
				</svg>
				Back to Home
			</a>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="py-16 px-4">
			<div class="container mx-auto text-center">
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
					Frequently Asked <span class="text-purple-600">Questions</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Find answers to the most common questions about Meme Face. Can't find what you're looking for? 
					Contact our support team for personalized help.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- FAQ Section -->
		<section class="py-12 px-4">
			<div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<!-- General Questions -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">General Questions</h2>
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What is Meme Face?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Meme Face is the ultimate destination for discovering and sharing the internet's most hilarious meme faces. 
									We offer a vast collection of classic and viral meme faces that you can browse, download, and share for free.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Is Meme Face completely free?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Yes! All meme faces on our platform are completely free to download and use. 
									We believe in making meme culture accessible to everyone.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How many meme faces do you have?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									We currently have over 5,234 meme faces in our collection, and we're constantly adding new ones. 
									Our library includes everything from classic internet memes to modern viral sensations.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Download Questions -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Download & Usage</h2>
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How do I download meme faces?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Simply click on any meme face image to download it to your device. 
									The download will start automatically, and you can save it wherever you prefer.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What file formats are available?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Our meme faces are available in various formats including JPG, PNG, GIF, and WebP. 
									The format depends on the original meme face and its animation requirements.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Can I use these meme faces commercially?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Most meme faces are free to use, but we recommend checking the original source and 
									respecting any copyright notices. Some meme faces may have specific usage restrictions.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Are there any usage restrictions?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Please use meme faces responsibly and respect others. Avoid using them for harassment, 
									hate speech, or other harmful purposes. Be mindful of context and audience.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Search & Navigation -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Search & Navigation</h2>
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How do I search for specific meme faces?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Use our search function to find meme faces by name, emotion, or keyword. 
									You can search for terms like "troll face", "rage guy", "surprised", or any emotion.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Can I browse by categories?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Yes! You can browse meme faces by emotion categories like happy, sad, angry, surprised, 
									and more. This makes it easy to find the perfect reaction for any situation.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How do I find popular meme faces?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Visit our homepage to see trending and classic meme faces that everyone loves. 
									These are the most downloaded and shared meme faces on our platform.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Technical Questions -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Technical Support</h2>
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">The website is loading slowly. What should I do?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Try refreshing the page, clearing your browser cache, or checking your internet connection. 
									If the problem persists, try accessing the site from a different device or browser.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Images aren't loading properly</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									This could be due to a slow internet connection, browser issues, or ad blockers. 
									Try disabling ad blockers temporarily or using a different browser.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Is Meme Face mobile-friendly?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Absolutely! Our website is fully optimized for mobile devices. 
									You can browse, search, and download meme faces on smartphones and tablets with ease.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Which browsers are supported?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									We support all modern browsers including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge. 
									For the best experience, make sure your browser is up to date.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Content Questions -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Content & Updates</h2>
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How often do you add new meme faces?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									We regularly update our collection with new meme faces. We add new content as soon as 
									we discover viral and trending meme faces that our community would love.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Can I request specific meme faces?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Yes! We welcome suggestions from our community. Contact us with your requests, 
									and we'll do our best to add the meme faces you're looking for.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Do you have meme faces from specific sources?</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600">
									Our collection includes meme faces from various sources including classic internet memes, 
									social media trends, and viral content. We strive to provide a diverse and comprehensive collection.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Contact Section -->
		<section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
			<div class="container mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
					Still Have <span class="text-purple-600">Questions?</span>
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					If you couldn't find the answer to your question here, our support team is ready to help you.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
					<a href="/help" class="bg-purple-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors">
						Get Help
					</a>
					<a href="/contact" class="bg-gray-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
						Contact Us
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout> 